
FEATURES
- 64bit host and/or guest support
- make Karma a server (e.g. provide a filesystem for l4re apps)
- systems debugger
- snapshots, migration
- support for systems without hardware assisted CPU virtualization (e.g. ARM)
- support for Cortex-A15
- implement VM halt

